{"tid":534402,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"老貓愈來愈瘦 有無咩食野建議？","createTime":"2018-01-19T18:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-20T04:57:31.000Z","uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"19abba5fb54927f21f47d152455f4fb3a54dccb4","tid":534402,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T18:11:52.000Z","msg":"我隻貓14歲啦 係唐貓所以都叫食得訓得走得<br />\n<br />\n但問題係佢好好胃口 一日4罐貓糧 <br />\n<br />\n以前細個唔識野 以為濕糧好啲 縱慣左佢 佢而家挨餓都唔食乾糧<br />\n<br />\n但食野愈來愈多 個身愈來愈輕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我餵過煮熟雞柳比佢 佢又唔多like<br />\n<br />\n請問有無其他食物高蛋白質 可以草返肥佢？<br />\n<br />\n生食我擔心佢十幾年食開熟野 咁老比生食會死左"},{"pid":"abe5e6b98877ebd2e99645e90e20178d7dee557d","tid":534402,"uid":6288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T18:36:04.000Z","msg":"你餵開邊隻濕糧？"},{"pid":"256c10675b54230d0433c02c843f6c392bee9771","tid":534402,"uid":43041,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T18:38:58.000Z","msg":"體重問題睇過獸醫未？咁老先黎轉糧問下醫生好d"},{"pid":"f3c39918f36d57d33d76c34f89aed06f53b75bd5","tid":534402,"uid":9412,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T18:44:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOz7W0VH--2WlqAE_3jtL4w/videos\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCOz7W0VH--2WlqAE_3jtL4w%2Fvideos&d=jgwfxsZ53oHshNhi0wrQjkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=2f9f05fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCOz7W0VH--2WlqAE_3jtL4w/videos</a><br />\n<br />\n學下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cd650440e5392aa9b9497d44d3b8e883748903d","tid":534402,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"abe5e6b98877ebd2e99645e90e20178d7dee557d","tid":534402,"uid":6288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T18:36:04.000Z","msg":"你餵開邊隻濕糧？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"